creator: Sokosawa Inc
descriptionHtml:
Sokosawa is one of the largest free online marketplace and classified app in Kenya

We provide a convenient, user friendly and secure platform for both sellers and buyers

How to post an ad on Sokosawa

Click on "POST FREE AD"
Create user account
Select your ad package and follow the steps - you can select free or paid package
Add your ad details; Ad description, price type, category, photos, item condition, bidding option, location and phone number
complete phone verification and submit ad for approval
How to buy on Sokosawa

Search for item
Contact seller via WhatsApp or message
Complete transaction outside of Sokosawa platform
Give the seller a thumbs up or five stars if they deserve it!
Safety

We are highly focused on safety. We require phone verification for all our platform users before conducting any business. If you run into any problems with a seller or suspect illegal activities or post, press "report" button to notify us. We will investigate and remove them from our platform if found in violation

Personal safety tips

Never pay for any services in advance
Always meet in a safe public location
Verify the condition of the item before closing the deal
Pay only after collecting the item
Never make hurried purchases or deals
You are solely responsible for your safety online - be vigilant
How to post like a pro!

Make good photos of your item
Provide prompt feedback to client calls or messages
